title: Devdutt Pattanaik - Collection [9 books]
description:
The Books in this Collection include:

1. 99 Thoughts on Ganesha
2. Business Sutra: A Very Indian Approach to Management
3. Indian Mythology
4. Jaya: An Illustrated Retelling of the Mahabharata
5. My Gita
6. Seven Secrets of Shiva
7. Shikhandi: And Other Tales They Don't Tell You
8. Sita: An Illustrated Retelling of the Ramayana 
9. The Goddess in India

Author: Devdutt Pattanaik
Format: ePub & Mobi
